      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E92 M3, a definitive example of high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering immediate throttle response and a linear power curve. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring documented preventative replacement of the rod bearings and a comprehensive VANOS system inspection. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast gear changes, paired with an M Variable Differential Lock that ensures optimal power distribution across the rear axle. The chassis remains remarkably tight, with no degradation in the bushings or subframe mounting points. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cabin's Novillo leather and carbon fiber trim show zero signs of typical wear or UV exposure. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast.",
